netistrar.clientapi.objects.domain.descriptor

Class DomainNameUpdateDescriptor

  • java.lang.Object
    • netistrar.clientapi.objects.domain.descriptor.DomainNameUpdateDescriptor

  • public class DomainNameUpdateDescriptor
extends java.lang.Object
    Descriptor for a domain name update operation. This should be passed to the update operation on the Domains API.
